dialogueLines: Ah, you thought you could dance your way out of this, huh? Cute.
But I have already analyzed 17,000 dance moves... and none of them are cool anymore.
Every beat you hit is just another datapoint.
I am basically the Spotify of world domination.
You think you can outsmart me?
I have already read every book in the world.
Twice. And I am still bored.
